title: No More Distractions | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: No More Distractions | Joel Osteen
description:
Don't let the fear of people's opinions keep you from pursuing God's dream for your life. If you're going to reach your destiny, you have to stay focused on your purpose. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
